text: haey puokke( puok kmean chomnue) niyeay tha hetoaveibeanchea ke minban banhchouh aoy ke( mou ham meat) nouv phosdo tang namuoy pi mcheasa robsa ke? dau che neah chaur anak( mou ham meat) tb vinh tha pitabrakd nasa brakear athrkambang ku samreab a l laoh temuoyokt dau che neah chaur puok anak rngcha( kar katkdei pi trong)choh pitabrakd nasa khnhom ka sthet knong chamnaom anak del rngcham meul cheamuoy puok anak der
